metadata.name: Photosynthesis
metadata.description:
Assimilation by biology, immersion and integration.

By view you are two, by process you are one. Undone without it, what would you become?  

You need it.
-

COLLECTOR BENEFITS;

- Cahaya aims to reinvest in local Balinese artisans by commissioning painters from Penestanan Village or Singaraja City to render their acquired piece on canvas using traditional mediums in A4 size or smaller - shipped worldwide.

- Original collector will also receive a limited 1 of 5 edition AIRDROP once the collection has sold out.

- The original collector also has the option to receive a fine art print in 11" x 14" or less, if they do not wish to receive an original Balinese painting - shipped worldwide.
